---
---

<section class="philosophy">
  <div class="philosophy-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="philosophy-inner container-wide">
    <blockquote>
      <p>We believe a garden should give back, to the land, to the community, and to everyone who walks its paths.</p>
    </blockquote>
    <p class="philosophy-body">Locally sourced plants, endemic species propagation, and a commitment to sustainable practice across Dominica's Nature Island.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="text-link text-link--light">Our approach</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .philosophy {
    position: relative;
    padding: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 9rem) 0;
    color: var(--white);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .philosophy-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: url('/images/pvalley.jpg') center / cover no-repeat;
  }

  .philosophy-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(12, 40, 30, 0.82);
  }

  .philosophy-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 54rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  blockquote {
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
  }

  blockquote p {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .philosophy-body {
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    max-width: 52ch;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) and (min-width: 1025px) {
    .philosophy-bg { background-attachment: fixed; }
  }
</style>
